 />\n睇到好撚尷尬</blockquote><br />\n我係條女見到呢啲肯定直接block<br />\nSorry都無句仲要講其他野扮無事<br />\n<br />\n直接啲：<br />\n對唔住呀我以後唔會放你飛機喇，唔好唔理我啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n道歉承諾無下次就一定要咖喇<br />\n逃避問題扮無野根本無解決過仲嬲多啲<br />\n但我覺得道完歉等佢無咁嬲講下白痴野都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時女仔係下完啖氣唔知點落堂 點變返平時咁<br />\n講下白痴野係幾有用，不過真係要處理咗件事先，唔係一嚟就扮無野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20f7d3b45e00b7e85a11f6380dbb60fc567ff296","tid":433450,"uid":20696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T14:45:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係樓下等左成個鐘好撚眼訓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢唔見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"3ef11dcaa298e8d0cc465b3bf69ef2ba90b9890c","tid":433450,"uid":3180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T14:45:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係樓下等左成個鐘好撚眼訓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n何必呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過洗濕左個頭就要等埋落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d20755e0ced68291334544b7cde49173bbac23dd","tid":433450,"uid":22243,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T14:47:27.000Z","msg":"我就6日冷戰後無左個女朋友<br />\n係愛既 記得做主動 人會心淡 嗌交每對情侶都有<br />\n點樣處理得好 就係你地既演繹方法"},{"pid":"075b64207747f5cae61827f37fed0a471416a2c7","tid":433450,"uid":5806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T14:49:09.000Z","msg":"如果佢唔肯見你就真係冇機了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打比佢同佢講啦<br />\n一齊返就唔好再有下次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"706cab3b3ffbb74c63312efa05dd59d34bad1cba","tid":433450,"uid":81287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci