ckquote>放飛機真係好撚黑人憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁前一晚都有同佢講嚟唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb3888f25194088533e78d59fd9be9eef5f701be","tid":433450,"uid":72943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T18:56:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一疊一千蚊錢車落佢面到<br />\n大罵一句  拎去洗啦臭雞<br />\n佢即刻收皮冧曬</blockquote><br />\n利申：窮撚<br />\n轉做一疊十蚊就得</blockquote><br />\n十蚊銀可能感覺會好d"},{"pid":"6d1c1e56f2cfe78475059b1cdf38f95a57e4a74b","tid":433450,"uid":153034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T19:46:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>問下啲白痴問題<br />\n「有無掛住我呀」<br />\n「你知唔知我最愛邊個英文字」（睇佢答唔答你）「係U(you)」<br />\n睇下佢受唔受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過冷乜鬼野戰呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要傾返計就直接打電話搵人 仲等message傻的嗎 睇字同聽聲唔同架</blockquote><br />\n睇到好撚尷尬</blockquote><br />\n我係條女見到呢啲肯定直接block<br />\nSorry都無句仲要講其他野扮無事<br />\n<br />\n直接啲：<br />\n對唔住呀我以後唔會放你飛機喇，唔好唔理我啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我反而直接啲嘅道歉 喺通知見到都廢事撳入去 心入面諗無下次就緊㗎啦 講埋啲廢話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有時可能條女都已經無嬲 你仲以為佢嬲緊喺度道歉 條女會覺得煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最好製造啲機會俾個位佢易落台 無落台位而一味道歉 一嚟條女唔受氹 二嚟男嘅會覺得「臭雞 歉都道撚左啦 仲想我點」 。女仔心入面嘅「氹」其實就係你講返啲野/專登去買佢中意食嘅野俾佢食 令佢條氣鋸返開心返 男仔我唔知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我男朋友覺得道左歉就係氹左我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n佢仲肯嬲你即係無事啦 不過係咁咦講返一兩句sorry都要嘅 plan好星期日帶佢去邊然後同佢講補返數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3bda7790b1c3874e13f3e25a0cb9cc37e3a6e55","tid":433450,"uid":81287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T09:54:02.000Z","msg":"我宣布已分手"},{"pid":"ae192182ddad320682f4c158ef615ad79930fdd1","tid":433450,"uid":70159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T10:09:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我宣布已分手</blockquote><br />\n有冇好似我教咁<br />\n至少賺番一句話啦"},{"pid":"6fd9823aeb3368a48f1b363ef2985d20425249a3","tid":433450,"uid":45195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T10:09:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>星期日本黎去邊架 ?</blockquote><br />\n沙灘，但佢黎m，之後話西九</blockquote><br />\n齋行街呀 ?</blockquote><br />\n西九文化區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有咩行"},{"pid":"de6e3d482283e7ac4ece9c22a3c3476724085c27","tid":433450,"uid":12111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T10:14:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我宣布已分手</blockquote><br />\n咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}